{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","data":{"alias":"metal-fusible-unicorn","description":"# Remediate CLAUDE.local.md to machine/operator-local content only\n\n## Why\n\n`CLAUDE.local.md` (155 lines) currently mixes two things: genuinely machine/operator-local\ncontent (this host's hourly `origin/main`-tracking LaunchAgent; the Gerrit credential\nidentities `RebarBotNava`/`JoeOakhartNava` and keychain specifics) and generally-applicable\nproject rules that are duplicated from `CLAUDE.md` (worktree discipline, activate-the-venv,\nplan-review signing, CI-before-close, the rebar tracking loop, a restatement of the Gerrit\nworkflow). The generally-applicable rules belong in the shared, checked-in guidance so every\nagent gets them; the local file should hold only what is specific to THIS machine/operator.\n\n## What\n\nStrip `CLAUDE.local.md` down to only machine/operator-local content, having first confirmed\n(via the AGENTS.md story) that every generally-applicable rule removed now lives in `AGENTS.md`\nor `docs/`. Keep: the local main-tracking LaunchAgent note and the Gerrit auth identities /\ncredential-pinning guidance. Optionally note that Anthropic now deprecates the `CLAUDE.local.md`\nname in favor of importing a gitignored file via `@` — record whether we adopt that or keep the\ncurrent name (a coherence decision, not required by this story).\n\n## Scope\n\nIn: `CLAUDE.local.md` only (git-ignored, local). Out: adding new content to `AGENTS.md`/`docs`\n(that is the AGENTS.md and re-home stories — this story only removes what they already re-homed).\nDepends on: the AGENTS.md story (the generally-applicable rules must have a home before removal).\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] `CLAUDE.local.md` contains only machine/operator-local content (main-tracking LaunchAgent\n  + Gerrit identities/credential pinning); no duplicated project-workflow guidance remains.\n  - Proving: reviewer confirms; `rg -c 'worktree|plan review|Track all work' CLAUDE.local.md`\n    trends to 0 for the generally-applicable rules.\n- [ ] Every rule removed has a verified home in `AGENTS.md` or `docs/` (no guidance lost).\n  - Proving: for each removed rule, cite the `AGENTS.md`/`docs` location in the change description.\n- [ ] Decision on the `CLAUDE.local.md`-name-vs-gitignored-`@import` modernization is recorded.","id":"955c-7a98-2485-4209","parent_id":"81e2-ad5e-bfe2-4653","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"story","title":"Remediate CLAUDE.local.md to machine/operator-local content only"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1784230956988271001,"uuid":"580a231c-dce5-4038-bf1f-0440fbf085b2"}